ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce de Bouctouche (New Brunswick) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE BOUCTOUCHE, in New Brunswick, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the Parish of Bouctouche to the Kent-Sud region including more specifically the following local service districts: Grande-Digue, Cocagne, Dundas, Grand Saint-Antoine, Saint-Antoine, Ste-Mary, Saint-Paul, Wellington, Bouctouche et Sainte-Anne.
